result.name: 臻味豬扒酸辣米線

reviews.text:
A new delicious noodles place spotted after a Sunday yoga class in APM. It’s only less than 10 minutes walk from the shopping mall.

For HKD$36, I was surprised that I could get this much pork chop and noodles! I love the sour and spicy soup base. Most of the times it’s only sour but not spicy for this kind of soup base, but this time I have a numbing spicy and sour one. Good job!

The pork chop was amazing too! There were so many pieces of it! Love it! They are so tender, flavoured and meaty! Not bony at all!

The whole bowl filled my tummy with great satisfaction. I can already see how frequent I would visit it in the future!
Love the spicy porkchop
veryvery salty soup...
Unparalleled numb & spicy
Good

result.name: 臻味豬扒酸辣米線

reviews.text:
A new delicious noodles place spotted after a Sunday yoga class in APM. It’s only less than 10 minutes walk from the shopping mall.

For HKD$36, I was surprised that I could get this much pork chop and noodles! I love the sour and spicy soup base. Most of the times it’s only sour but not spicy for this kind of soup base, but this time I have a numbing spicy and sour one. Good job!

The pork chop was amazing too! There were so many pieces of it! Love it! They are so tender, flavoured and meaty! Not bony at all!

The whole bowl filled my tummy with great satisfaction. I can already see how frequent I would visit it in the future!

米線，麵，都大大碗。
價錢/味道都係普通茶餐廳質素，圓枱多，坐得唔迫。
在官塘行街頭岳岳，輔警叔叔問有什麼可幫到你? 我說正在找好吃的，他馬上介紹這家食肆😄。之後去官塘行街，很多時都去臻味👍
超級好味！食完上隱！ I am addicted to it.
今時今日，4拾蚊，甘大碗，用料有足，食材新鮮，合格有餘。叫套餐包飲野，唔叫套餐多好多好野食，最後一句，每星期來三四次都冇問題，好食。
